Sample Date.description: The date when the wastewater samples were collected from the Deer Island wastewater treatment plant in Massachusetts.

North System Flows to DITP, MGD.col_name: North System Flows to DITP, MGD
North System Flows to DITP, MGD.description: The daily flow rate of the northern influent stream to the Deer Island wastewater treatment plant in Massachusetts.

South System Flows to DITP, MGD.col_name: South System Flows to DITP, MGD
South System Flows to DITP, MGD.description: The daily flow rate of the southern influent stream to the Deer Island wastewater treatment plant in Massachusetts.

Total flows to DITP (MGD: Million gallon.col_name: Total flows to DITP (MGD: Million gallon per day)
Total flows to DITP (MGD: Million gallon.description: The total daily flow rate to the Deer Island wastewater treatment plant in Massachusetts, which is the sum of the flow rates of the northern and southern influents.
